lsgpu (0.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * NVIDIA stats via nvidia-smi
  * AMD stats via sysfs
  * GPU process listing
  * Real-time monitoring with sparklines (--watch)
  * EDID monitor identification
  * Override file support
  * Connected-only default (-a for all)

